701081.text: 1. This game is an easy-to-play RPG & SLG game, suitable for users of 16 years and above. It is recommended that minors are supervised by a parent or guardian when using this game. $B$$B$2. This game is based on a fictional background storyline that uses western fantasy concepts with a simple and positive narrative. A portion of the characters have been adapted from reality but have been changed enough so as not to confuse anyone. The game encourages players to unlock the parts of the map and complete stage quests in order to help the Witch that has lost her memory to retrieve it again. There is a text-based social networking system within the game that allows players to communicate with strangers. The system's management adheres to all of the required related laws. $B$$B$3. This game has a real-name authentication system, all minors on the system will be restricted by the in-game management as follows: Some gameplay modes and items require payment, minors under 8 years of age will not be able to pay for these. Minors over 8 years of age, but under 16 years of age cannot top up more than 50 RMB at one time and their monthly top ups cannot exceed 200 RMB. Minors over 16 years of age cannot top up more than 100 RMB at one time and their monthly top ups cannot exceed 400 RMB. Minors will not be able to player the game each day from between the hours of 22:00 - 08:00, and will not be able to play fro more than 3 hours per day during public holidays and 1.5 hours per day the rest of the time. $B$$B$4. This game's gameplay is primarily based on strategy and battle, while also having many puzzle elements in the maps that will aid players in training their logical reasoning skills and hand-eye coordination in order to provide a happy and positive experience to players. The game has a unique artistic graphical style, with many finely-drawn character portraits and figures and well-polished maps that help to improve players' own aesthetic intelligence.
